{"tid":1743620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【MAX觀點】《香港人權與民主法案》極速過關 全靠佩洛西「奇招」","createTime":"2019-11-21T09:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T04:37:17.000Z","uid":193217,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"685df46b0f010278c44ace9ec7a2d7512a7674e8","tid":1743620,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國眾議院通過參議院版本的《香港人權與民主法案》，法案待總統特朗普簽署後，便會正式生效。<br />\n<br />\n《時事全方位》主持王慧麟指，今次眾議院在參議院通過法案後翌日，便通過參議院版本的法案，實屬罕見。他解釋，參眾兩院互相制衡，一般而言，參議院通過的法案版本較眾議院保守，眾議院通常需時磋商一個中間方案，以取得兩院共識。<br />\n<br />\n王慧麟指，眾議院近日正處理特朗普「通烏門」的彈劾議案，在事件發酵之際，眾議院議長佩洛西突然出「奇招」，將參議院版本的《香港人權與民主法案》全盤接收，直接付諸表決，令法案在民主共和兩黨成員壓倒性支持下極速通過。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，除非總統事前已表明不簽署法案，否則法案在兩黨共同支持下，特朗普通常必定會簽署法案，以免損害行政立法關係，甚至波及共和黨員對彈劾特朗普議案的取態。因此，法案何時正式生效，大家可拭目以待&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n多謝民主女神佩洛西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4f07a765dac502ee3b16a0de167e3b9a3cee58","tid":1743620,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:37:58.000Z","msg":"左膠但要多謝"},{"pid":"1993f3bf2dc47a3712771305e41bb966d1dbc896","tid":1743620,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"今次直情唔洗討論協商<br />\n直接限40分鍾.場波未波已經投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要幾憎共產黨先做得出<br />\n大家都知眾議會同參議會傾協商都至少成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514ad91e219763d54b854a60fa842865ef5a0a0a","tid":1743620,"uid":165336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2c4f07a765dac502ee3b16a0de167e3b9a3cee58","tid":1743620,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:37:58.000Z","msg":"左膠但要多謝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"正正就係因為左膠先會幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723827571f47e82817344af0f2319c693a03b1c7","tid":1743620,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:46:08.000Z","msg":"Thank you Pelosi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n64個陣佢係現場<br />\n唔憎中共就奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7866e1df70e1131f8a7edc27fd726abb9bc56b2b","tid":1743620,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c4f07a765dac502ee3b16a0de167e3b9a3cee58","tid":1743620,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:37:58.000Z","msg":"左膠但要多謝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"真。勇武左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c718f953068ffdb7a8babe6a68bd42aa7f4af16b","tid":1743620,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:37:17.000Z","msg":"(最新update)感謝祭漏網系列：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<br />\nSpeaker Nancy Pelosi 簽署<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi/status/1197561007763337216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpeakerPelosi%2Fstatus%2F1197561007763337216&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=54d5fc55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpeakerPelosi%2Fstatus%2F1197561007763337216&h=6621fd04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi/status/1197561007763337216</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Chuck Grassley <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChuckGrassley/status/1197609025086480384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChuckGrassley%2Fstatus%